{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1364,"text":"I just met you on a bus,"},{"time":4637,"text":"and we would really like \nto get to know each other,"},{"time":7078,"text":"but I've got to get off at the next stop,"},{"time":9564,"text":"so you're going to tell me \nthree things about yourself"},{"time":14331,"text":"that just define you as a person,"},{"time":17911,"text":"three things about yourself"},{"time":19689,"text":"that will help me understand who you are,"},{"time":23298,"text":"three things that just \nget to your very essence."},{"time":27292,"text":"And what I'm wondering"},{"time":30370,"text":"is, of those three things,"},{"time":33659,"text":"is any one of them"},{"time":35649,"text":"surviving some kind of trauma?"},{"time":40673,"text":"Cancer survivor, rape survivor,"},{"time":46370,"text":"Holocaust survivor, incest survivor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":51487,"text":"Ever notice how we tend to identify ourselves"},{"time":54931,"text":"by our wounds?"},{"time":57462,"text":"And where I have seen this survivor identity"},{"time":61938,"text":"have the most consequences"},{"time":64426,"text":"is in the cancer community."},{"time":66979,"text":"And I've been around this \ncommunity for a long time,"},{"time":69713,"text":"because I've been a hospice \nand a hospital chaplain"},{"time":72907,"text":"for almost 30 years."},{"time":76204,"text":"And in 2005, I was working at a big cancer center"},{"time":81937,"text":"when I received the news that"},{"time":84242,"text":"my mother had breast cancer."},{"time":87677,"text":"And then five days later,"},{"time":89859,"text":"I received the news that I had breast cancer."},{"time":95326,"text":"My mother and I can be competitive —"},{"time":97959,"text":"(Laughter) —"},{"time":99747,"text":"but I was really not trying to\ncompete with her on this one."},{"time":104179,"text":"And in fact, I thought, well,"},{"time":106204,"text":"if you have to have cancer,"},{"time":108139,"text":"it's pretty convenient to be working"},{"time":109860,"text":"at a place that treats it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111371,"text":"But this is what I heard from \na lot of outraged people."},{"time":114068,"text":"What?"},{"time":115530,"text":"You're the chaplain."},{"time":117450,"text":"You should be immune."},{"time":119740,"text":"Like, maybe I should have just gotten off"},{"time":121817,"text":"with a warning instead of an actual ticket,"},{"time":124112,"text":"because I'm on the force."},{"time":127880,"text":"So I did get my treatment at the\ncancer center where I worked,"},{"time":130855,"text":"which was amazingly convenient,"},{"time":133376,"text":"and I had chemotherapy"},{"time":135615,"text":"and a mastectomy, and a saline implant put in,"},{"time":138325,"text":"and so before I say another word,\nlet me just say right now,"},{"time":140450,"text":"this is the fake one. (Laughter)"},{"time":145224,"text":"I have found that I need to get that out of the way,"},{"time":148437,"text":"because I'll see somebody go"},{"time":150211,"text":"\"Oh, I know it's this one.\""},{"time":152428,"text":"And then I'll move or I'll \ngesture and they'll go,"},{"time":154892,"text":"\"No, it's that one.\""},{"time":157445,"text":"So now you know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":159616,"text":"I learned a lot being a patient,"},{"time":161753,"text":"and one of the surprising things was"},{"time":163275,"text":"that only a small part of the cancer experience"},{"time":167382,"text":"is about medicine."},{"time":169474,"text":"Most of it is about feelings and faith"},{"time":173827,"text":"and losing and finding your identity"},{"time":176460,"text":"and discovering strength"},{"time":178038,"text":"and flexibility you never even knew you had."},{"time":181960,"text":"It's about realizing that"},{"time":184289,"text":"the most important things in life are"},{"time":187359,"text":"not things at all, but relationships,"},{"time":190440,"text":"and it's about laughing in the face of uncertainty"},{"time":194506,"text":"and learning that the way to\nget out of almost anything"},{"time":197945,"text":"is to say, \"I have cancer.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":202260,"text":"So the other thing I learned was that"},{"time":204773,"text":"I don't have to take on \"cancer survivor\""},{"time":208227,"text":"as my identity,"},{"time":210195,"text":"but, boy, are there powerful forces"},{"time":213814,"text":"pushing me to do just that."},{"time":217360,"text":"Now, don't, please, misunderstand me."},{"time":221678,"text":"Cancer organizations"},{"time":223637,"text":"and the drive for early screening"},{"time":225617,"text":"and cancer awareness and cancer research"},{"time":228271,"text":"have normalized cancer,"},{"time":230386,"text":"and this is a wonderful thing."},{"time":231710,"text":"We can now talk about cancer"},{"time":233794,"text":"without whispering."},{"time":235572,"text":"We can talk about cancer and\nwe can support one another."},{"time":240090,"text":"But sometimes, it feels"},{"time":243176,"text":"like people go a little overboard"},{"time":244574,"text":"and they start telling us how we're going to feel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249779,"text":"So about a week after my surgery,"},{"time":253322,"text":"we had a houseguest."},{"time":256202,"text":"That was probably our first mistake."},{"time":258950,"text":"And keep in mind that"},{"time":260471,"text":"at this point in my life"},{"time":262141,"text":"I had been a chaplain for over 20 years,"},{"time":265763,"text":"and issues like dying and death"},{"time":268086,"text":"and the meaning of life,"},{"time":269642,"text":"these are all things I'd been \nyakking about forever."},{"time":272820,"text":"So at dinner that night,"},{"time":275320,"text":"our houseguest proceeds to\nstretch his arms up over his head,"},{"time":278056,"text":"and say, \"You know, Deb,"},{"time":280861,"text":"now you're really going to learn what's important."},{"time":285010,"text":"Yes, you are going to make some big changes"},{"time":287707,"text":"in your life,"},{"time":289077,"text":"and now you're going to start\nthinking about your death."},{"time":292725,"text":"Yep, this cancer is your wakeup call.\""},{"time":298520,"text":"Now, these are golden words"},{"time":301175,"text":"coming from someone who is speaking about"},{"time":303154,"text":"their own experience,"},{"time":305573,"text":"but when someone is telling you"},{"time":307949,"text":"how you are going to feel,"},{"time":310342,"text":"it's instant crap."},{"time":312388,"text":"The only reason I did not kill him"},{"time":315292,"text":"with my bare hands"},{"time":317283,"text":"was because I could not lift my right arm."},{"time":321378,"text":"But I did say a really bad word to him,"},{"time":325596,"text":"followed by a regular word, that —"},{"time":328497,"text":"(Laughter) —"},{"time":329720,"text":"made my husband say, \"She's on narcotics.\""},{"time":333238,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":335196,"text":"And then after my treatment, it just felt like"},{"time":337690,"text":"everyone was telling me what my\nexperience was going to mean."},{"time":340973,"text":"\"Oh, this means you're going to be doing the walk.\""},{"time":343765,"text":"\"Oh, this means you're coming to the luncheon.\""},{"time":345389,"text":"\"This means you're going to be wearing"},{"time":346651,"text":"the pink ribbon and the pink t-shirt"},{"time":349042,"text":"and the headband and the earrings"},{"time":350904,"text":"and the bracelet and the panties.\""},{"time":354640,"text":"Panties. No, seriously, google it."},{"time":357869,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":359920,"text":"How is that raising awareness?"},{"time":362011,"text":"Only my husband should be seeing my panties."},{"time":364078,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":365747,"text":"He's pretty aware of cancer already."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370158,"text":"It was at that point where I felt like, oh my God,"},{"time":373302,"text":"this is just taking over my life."},{"time":376452,"text":"And that's when I told myself, \nclaim your experience."},{"time":381424,"text":"Don't let it claim you."},{"time":385086,"text":"We all know that"},{"time":387194,"text":"the way to cope with trauma, with loss,"},{"time":391316,"text":"with any life-changing experience,"},{"time":393741,"text":"is to find meaning."},{"time":395891,"text":"But here's the thing:"},{"time":398128,"text":"No one can tell us"},{"time":399795,"text":"what our experience means."},{"time":402531,"text":"We have to decide what it means."},{"time":405820,"text":"And it doesn't have to be some gigantic,"},{"time":407952,"text":"extroverted meaning."},{"time":409959,"text":"We don't all have to start a foundation"},{"time":412470,"text":"or an organization or write a book"},{"time":414622,"text":"or make a documentary."},{"time":417502,"text":"Meaning can be quiet"},{"time":420449,"text":"and introverted."},{"time":422620,"text":"Maybe we make one small decision about our lives"},{"time":428548,"text":"that can bring about big change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433626,"text":"Many years ago, I had a patient,"},{"time":435566,"text":"just a wonderful young man"},{"time":437571,"text":"who was loved by the staff,"},{"time":440306,"text":"and so it was something of a shock to us to realize"},{"time":443190,"text":"that he had no friends."},{"time":446974,"text":"He lived by himself,"},{"time":449280,"text":"he would come in for chemotherapy by himself,"},{"time":453308,"text":"he would receive his treatment,"},{"time":455253,"text":"and then he'd walk home alone."},{"time":458984,"text":"And I even asked him. I said, \"Hey,"},{"time":460748,"text":"how come you never bring a friend with you?\""},{"time":463489,"text":"And he said, \"I don't really have any friends.\""},{"time":468208,"text":"But he had tons of friends on the infusion floor."},{"time":470469,"text":"We all loved him, and people were going\nin and out of his room all the time."},{"time":474845,"text":"So at his last chemo,"},{"time":477804,"text":"we sang him the song"},{"time":479131,"text":"and we put the crown on his \nhead and we blew the bubbles,"},{"time":481898,"text":"and then I asked him, I said,"},{"time":484339,"text":"\"So what are you going to do now?\""},{"time":488795,"text":"And he answered,"},{"time":490605,"text":"\"Make friends.\""},{"time":492238,"text":"And he did."},{"time":494350,"text":"He started volunteering \nand he made friends there,"},{"time":497904,"text":"and he began going to a church\nand he made friends there,"},{"time":500590,"text":"and at Christmas he invited my husband\nand me to a party in his apartment,"},{"time":503550,"text":"and the place was filled with his friends."},{"time":508667,"text":"Claim your experience."},{"time":510910,"text":"Don't let it claim you."},{"time":512559,"text":"He decided that the meaning of his experience"},{"time":517431,"text":"was to know the joy of friendship,"},{"time":521198,"text":"and then learn to make friends."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525806,"text":"So what about you?"},{"time":529792,"text":"How are you going to find meaning"},{"time":532145,"text":"in your crappy experience?"},{"time":534592,"text":"It could be a recent one,"},{"time":536483,"text":"or it could be one that you've been carrying around"},{"time":538454,"text":"for a really long time."},{"time":542345,"text":"It's never too late to change what it means,"},{"time":546855,"text":"because meaning is dynamic."},{"time":549110,"text":"What it means today"},{"time":550771,"text":"may not be what it means a year from now,"},{"time":552698,"text":"or 10 years from now."},{"time":555541,"text":"It's never too late to become someone other"},{"time":558151,"text":"than simply a survivor."},{"time":561672,"text":"Hear how static that word sounds?"},{"time":564996,"text":"Survivor."},{"time":566913,"text":"No movement, no growth."},{"time":571304,"text":"Claim your experience."},{"time":573191,"text":"Don't let it claim you, because if you do,"},{"time":575812,"text":"I believe you will become trapped,"},{"time":578973,"text":"you will not grow, you will not evolve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584915,"text":"But of course, sometimes it's not outside pressures"},{"time":588393,"text":"that cause us to take on that identity of survivor."},{"time":592764,"text":"Sometimes we just like the perks."},{"time":596657,"text":"Sometimes there's a payoff."},{"time":600165,"text":"But then we get stuck."},{"time":603900,"text":"Now, one of the first things I learned"},{"time":605711,"text":"as a chaplain intern was the three C's"},{"time":609817,"text":"of the chaplain's job:"},{"time":612208,"text":"Comfort, clarify and, when necessary, confront"},{"time":619170,"text":"or challenge."},{"time":621325,"text":"Now, we all pretty much love the comforting"},{"time":623271,"text":"and the clarifying."},{"time":625128,"text":"The confronting, not so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":630070,"text":"One of the other things that I loved"},{"time":632064,"text":"about being a chaplain was"},{"time":634522,"text":"seeing patients a year, or even several years"},{"time":638995,"text":"after their treatment, because"},{"time":640836,"text":"it was just really cool to see \nhow they had changed"},{"time":643536,"text":"and how their lives had evolved"},{"time":645752,"text":"and what had happened to them."},{"time":647642,"text":"So I was thrilled one day"},{"time":650162,"text":"to get a page down into the lobby of the clinic"},{"time":652610,"text":"from a patient who I had seen the year before,"},{"time":656191,"text":"and she was there with her two adult daughters,"},{"time":658665,"text":"who I also knew, for her one year follow-up exam."},{"time":662924,"text":"So I got down to the lobby, and they were ecstatic"},{"time":666461,"text":"because she had just gotten\nall of her test results back"},{"time":668712,"text":"and she was NED: No Evidence of Disease."},{"time":674900,"text":"Which I used to think meant Not Entirely Dead."},{"time":679657,"text":"So they were ecstatic, we sat down to visit,"},{"time":685150,"text":"and it was so weird, because"},{"time":687957,"text":"within two minutes, she \nstarted retelling me the story"},{"time":691839,"text":"of her diagnosis and her \nsurgery and her chemo,"},{"time":696369,"text":"even though, as her chaplain, \nI saw her every week,"},{"time":699837,"text":"and so I knew this story."},{"time":702728,"text":"And she was using words like suffering,"},{"time":705770,"text":"agony, struggle."},{"time":709765,"text":"And she ended her story with,"},{"time":712379,"text":"\"I felt crucified.\""},{"time":717173,"text":"And at that point, her two \ndaughters got up and said,"},{"time":719837,"text":"\"We're going to go get coffee.\""},{"time":723749,"text":"And they left."},{"time":726890,"text":"Tell me three things about\nyourself before the next stop."},{"time":729725,"text":"People were leaving the bus before she even got"},{"time":732481,"text":"to number two or number three."},{"time":737858,"text":"So I handed her a tissue,"},{"time":741345,"text":"and I gave her a hug,"},{"time":744642,"text":"and then, because I really cared for this woman,"},{"time":748152,"text":"I said,"},{"time":750238,"text":"\"Get down off your cross.\""},{"time":752544,"text":"And she said, \"What?\""},{"time":756810,"text":"And I repeated, \"Get down off your cross.\""},{"time":762224,"text":"And to her credit, she could \ntalk about her reasons"},{"time":766869,"text":"for embracing and then clinging to this identity."},{"time":771988,"text":"It got her a lot of attention."},{"time":774010,"text":"People were taking care of her for a change."},{"time":777115,"text":"But now, it was having the opposite effect."},{"time":780810,"text":"It was pushing people away."},{"time":783293,"text":"People kept leaving to get coffee."},{"time":787040,"text":"She felt crucified by her experience,"},{"time":790941,"text":"but she didn't want to let that crucified self die."},{"time":797163,"text":"Now, perhaps you are thinking"},{"time":800080,"text":"I was a little harsh with her,"},{"time":803030,"text":"so I must tell you that"},{"time":805138,"text":"I was speaking out of my own experience."},{"time":808830,"text":"Many, many years before,"},{"time":811674,"text":"I had been fired from a job that I loved,"},{"time":815000,"text":"and I would not stop talking about my innocence"},{"time":818716,"text":"and the injustice and the betrayal and the deceipt,"},{"time":822120,"text":"until finally, just like this woman,"},{"time":823250,"text":"people were walking away from me,"},{"time":825291,"text":"until I finally realized"},{"time":828527,"text":"I wasn't just processing my feelings,"},{"time":832399,"text":"I was feeding them."},{"time":835107,"text":"I didn't want to let that crucified self die."},{"time":839170,"text":"But we all know that with any resurrection story,"},{"time":844592,"text":"you have to die first."},{"time":847220,"text":"The Christian story,"},{"time":849043,"text":"Jesus was dead a whole day in the tomb"},{"time":852315,"text":"before he was resurrected."},{"time":854810,"text":"And I believe that for us,"},{"time":856648,"text":"being in the tomb"},{"time":858780,"text":"means doing our own deep inner work"},{"time":862766,"text":"around our wounds"},{"time":865470,"text":"and allowing ourselves to be healed."},{"time":869943,"text":"We have to let that crucified self die"},{"time":873000,"text":"so that a new self, a truer self,"},{"time":876604,"text":"is born."},{"time":878986,"text":"We have to let that old story go"},{"time":881844,"text":"so that a new story, a truer story,"},{"time":885991,"text":"can be told."},{"time":889030,"text":"Claim your experience. Don't let it claim you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":894573,"text":"What if there were no survivors,"},{"time":897154,"text":"meaning, what if people decided"},{"time":899950,"text":"to just claim their trauma as an experience"},{"time":902820,"text":"instead of taking it on as an identity?"},{"time":906990,"text":"Maybe it would be the end of being"},{"time":908992,"text":"trapped in our wounds"},{"time":911350,"text":"and the beginning of amazing"},{"time":914904,"text":"self-exploration and discovery and growth."},{"time":918830,"text":"Maybe it would be the start of defining ourselves"},{"time":923625,"text":"by who we have become"},{"time":926205,"text":"and who we are becoming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":930375,"text":"So perhaps survivor was not"},{"time":936146,"text":"one of the three things that you would tell me."},{"time":941353,"text":"No matter."},{"time":942670,"text":"I just want you all to know that"},{"time":944910,"text":"I am really glad that we are on this bus together,"},{"time":949223,"text":"and this is my stop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":953119,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}